{"tid":1882039,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府靠呢個濕鳩添馬台搞文宣戰，手足唔係唔做嘢呀？","createTime":"2020-02-16T03:46:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T03:47:02.000Z","uid":269265,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"11f497706b1eadb4006dfeca6438032c849e07a3","tid":1882039,"uid":269265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T03:46:14.000Z","msg":"傳媒踢爆警謊，佢就話人針對，<br />\n咁大家就一齊針對吓佢，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Report爆佢啦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/111887223633612/posts/142868340535500/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F111887223633612%2Fposts%2F142868340535500%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=sh6QB3P1ZXxG4EHsBexfbjJoBOSHi9wRld7hxL8G3jc%3D&h=5681b413\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/111887223633612/posts/142868340535500/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n添馬台<br />\n<br />\n【澄清】<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有傳媒針對警方</span></span>，質疑警方獲發口罩和保護衣的用量較其他紀律部隊或很多部門多。<br />\n<br />\n最簡單的理由是因為警隊人數達30000人，是各部門人數之最。警隊亦一直協助衞生署執行防疫工作，包括：在檢疫中心駐守、駐守口岸協助執行檢疫令、突擊檢查在家受檢疫人士等。<br />\n<br />\n此外，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警隊很多人員在工作期間會與市民接觸</span></span>。為確保警方為市民提供的服務不會受到影響，這些人員一般會獲分配口罩，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">保障警員和市民的健康。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我們早前已解釋過，任何前線人員，無論衞生署、食環署、警察、入境處、海關等，防護物資的分配都是按照他們的崗位和工作涉及的風險而訂定，並非由他們所屬部門而定。"},{"pid":"afddd7852d7d8a4162ebdf92425029176b083ed8","tid":1882039,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T03:47:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}